8 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現金回贈、手續費優惠</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貸款資金不受嚴格限制</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">🥊 稅貸比拼：恒生借得月薪倍數最高、還款期最長</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於一眾銀行及財務機構亦陸續推出各式各樣稅務貸款優惠，是大家一年一度借平錢的好機會，貸款用途不但可繳稅，更可用作其他財務需要，貸款額可高達月薪24倍或數百萬元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-07aadbeb-4477-4be0-a04b-73311b82837f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多間銀行已推出今年度稅貸優惠，包括：</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">↕️ 最高貸款金額（月薪倍數計）24倍：恒生銀行</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">↔️ 最長還款期60個月：恒生銀行、滙豐、東亞、花旗、MOX、中銀、UA</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，中銀已將優惠期延長至2026年1月5日；而眾安更推出加碼優惠，用戶只要每月維持指定賬戶結餘水平，即可賺取回贈，實際年利率最高可減3.99%，即有機會實現極具吸引力的0%實際年利率，惟成功門檻不低，詳情可參考下表眾安銀行的官網連結。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大家參考以下稅貸比拼表，比較優惠等詳情，表格內更附有各大銀行及金融機構稅貸官網專頁連結，可以一按即看官網詳情。</p><iframe height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://flo.uri.sh/visualisation/25887369/embed?auto=1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1.42\" title=\"Flourish chart\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>",
