            "title": "爆一爆｜電動車取消一換一 谷出恐懼式消費（Louise）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fZQLAG9LlZmKkts3bomLCQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/82c2ba50-14b2-11f1-b67b-1846139b3d52\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">年三十晚，富利堡車行老細Eric Wong來電，話已準備$20萬現金，實行年初一開鋪，雙倍奬償俾做到生意嘅sales，心諗使唔使咁搏呀？年初一都開舖？</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://yfinance.onelink.me/3068494570?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_[…]ub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub3=&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">猶如掟咗個炸彈落市場</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">認識Eric Wong逾30年，做生意嘅機動性極高，預算案取消電動車一換一優惠政策後，市場都來唔切反應，猶如掟咗個炸彈落電動車市場，佢老哥十足警隊機動部隊咁，即日有個心戰室War Room，其核心團隊聽住財爺宣讀預算案，一有消息就立即行動，當日即刻搞咗個通宵營業，將Sales分日更同埋夜更。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9cfea20d-2f44-44c9-9640-fe26cb1b5026-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">真係不得不佩服佢嘅市場觸覺，香港人有錯失恐懼症Fear of Missing Out (FOMO)，加上運輸署當日份新聞稿，令人誤以為落閘時間喺2月25日23：59，才享有一換一優惠，搞到有意換電車人士喺恐懼之下，半夜三更去車行出車。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"預算案公佈取消一換一，即時谷起「恐懼式消費」。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jPZmKI4sFUpbOgxOrYoI0A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/aa5afd20-14b2-11f1-9ffd-604022d347c3\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">預算案公佈取消一換一，即時谷起「恐懼式消費」。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Eric Wong 話: 「香港人嘅DNA 係走難就最快。有個客夜晚11：50分撲到來鋪頭，就猛咁鬧財爺cancel一換一，以為出唔到車。咁我哋女sales就解釋俾佢聽唔使咁嘮嘈，deadline 係三月底。但呢個客依然係媽媽有聲鬧運輸處唔講清楚。」</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">香港啲官一定緊貼國家政策</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三個月前佢老哥對於取消一換一已經有所準備，同上汽同廣汽的老總研判，押注香港啲官一定緊貼國家政策，睇到上年阿爺已取消對電車補貼，香港班官又點會唔照辦煮碗呢？之所以年初一照常營業賣車，谷得一部得一部。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預算案公佈取消一換一，即時谷起「恐懼式消費」，佢話已經入定貨500部廣汽和400部MG電動車，售完即止咁話，仲參考了股神巴菲特嘅名言「別人恐懼嘅時候，佢就要貪婪」啦！各位電動車準買家，好好消化呢句話了，而富利堡的團隊，在通宵營業後就搞咗個慶功宴齊歡唱，Eric Wong 則說：「三個月前嘅部儲，我瘦咗12磅呀！」</p></div>",
